<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, June 22 (YONHAP) -- The government will call 
a unification and national security policy coordination meeting 
Thursday morning to discuss strategy at a preliminary contact 
for the proposed inter-Korean summit and the formation of a 
delegation to the contact. 
  The meeting participants will draw up Seoul's position on 
