<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, June 21 (YONHAP) -- President Kim Yong-sam 
cabled a consolatory message to Chinese President Jiang Zemin on 
Tuesday in connection with the recent flood in southern China. 
  President Kim said he was grieved at the reports of the 
large 
losses of human lives and properties suffered in the flood, 
saying he was praying for early reliefs and rehabilitation. 

