<H3> <TI>   More on LDP's No-Confidence Motion </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    More on LDP's No-Confidence Motion </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2206084694 Tokyo KYODO in English 0843 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>
