<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, June 21, IRNA -- The ambassador of the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea (DPRK) here, K. Yong Roi, 
told managing director of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
Broadcasting (IRIB), 'Ali Larijani on Tuesday that the U.S. has 
private goals behind its avowed concern about nuclear 
proliferation, and that it exploits the U.N. as a platform for 
