needlessly difficult for DPRK. 
  He said DPRK is interested in talks with South Korea and 
that 
already many meetings have been held between the officials of 
the two Koreas. 
  Larijani said the Islamic Republic of Iran has valued its 
friendly relations with DPRK which, he said, is obviously 
annoying to the United States. 
  He said Iran would all the same continue to support the 
anti-imperialist position of the Democratic People's Republic of 
Korea. 

