<F P=100> Cambodia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Special Vietnamese Police Force Set Up </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Special Vietnamese Police Force Set Up </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2306033694 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2306033694 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia </F>

<F P=105>  Cambodian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Diplomatic sources in Phnom Penh say the 
communist Vietnam has set up another special police force named 
F-91. This group closely operates with the Second Bureau of the 
two-headed government army. This Vietnamese special force 
commands and give orders to all puppet troops. It gives orders 
to Ke Kimyan, Pol Saroeun and other men in the General Staff 
office. There are also Vietnamese giving orders behind the back 
of Tie Banh in the National Defense Ministry. These sources 
also specify that it is this Vietnamese special force that 
carries out arrests and the most barbarous executions of people. 
[passage omitted] 

