<H3> <TI>   Hanoi Delegation Arrives for Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hanoi Delegation Arrives for Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2206045594 Vientiane Vitthayou Hengsat Radio Network in 
Lao 0000 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2206045594 </F>
<F P=104>  Vientiane Vitthayou Hengsat Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Lao </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A delegation from the Hanoi Agricultural and 
Forestry Service of the SRV, headed by its chief Nguyen Ton Tao, 
arrived in Vientiane on 16 June along with a number of 
technicians to visit Laos at the invitation of Thongmi 
Phommisai, head of the of Vientiane Municipality Agricultural 
